License and provenance boundary for this repository

This repository is a mixed paper-data package. The terms below apply only where
the authors or repository maintainers control the rights.

Author-created repository documentation, package metadata, manifests, checksum
records, and data dictionaries are licensed under the Creative Commons
Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0):

https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

The Excel workbooks under `data/` were supplied by coauthor Yadi Wang for this
paper package and are preserved here as paper-specific derived-data evidence.
This repository does not assert a blanket reuse license over those workbooks
unless and until a separate coauthor/source-data license grant is documented.
Reuse of those workbooks should cite the paper and the repository provenance,
and should respect any terms that attach to the underlying project appraisal
documents, government patronage sources, travel-time measurements, planning
documents, or other source materials represented in the workbooks.

The proceedings PDF in `paper/` is included only as a local audit reference copy
and retains its publisher or repository terms. It is not relicensed here.

No MIT software license is asserted because this repository does not stage
paper-specific scripts, notebooks, model source code, or other executable
software.
